<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/2297284-ceevee">Ceevee</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I liked Ciro because he was a well-developed character with human frailties and strengths. He was tormented by his mother&apos;s/father&apos;s abandonment, yet <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I liked Ciro because he was a well-developed character with human frailties and strengths. He was tormented by his mother's/father's abandonment, yet did not cave-in. He thrived. He made the best of every situation. He struggled with religion but admitted it. He persevered in the presence of of difficulty. I admire his energy and ambition, as well as his love of family. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
