              <span id="reviewTextContainer411836913" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8943530121782642015">This book was written in such a fashion, it read like a movie. The description used to illustrate every movement allowed the movie to continue to play throughout my mind on every page. I fell in love with each of the characters, and their stories. It was so good, I read it in 4 days, staying up until 3 A.M. to find out what happened next!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


